V`Thanga Magal,' a cassette containing devotional hymns composed by S. Annapoorani and set to tuneful melodies by V.Kalyani, are sung by K. Bhuvaneswari, Hyderabad Sowmya, G.Sridhar, R.Manoharan, R.Vasanthavalli, Kalyani, Divyaa Ravichandran, and N.C. Kannan. The songs on Sri Aurobindo and Mira, the Divine Mother, in simple Tamil, have a heart-warming appeal.  The enjoyable keyboard music by Paul Christopher stands apart with its dignified style and substance. A Sadhana Group production priced at Rs 100.
